dc_description_s: Map shows: provincial boundary, district boundary, divisional boundary, divisional headquarters, motor roads, projected roads of the 1929 programme, native courts, native administration schools, native administration dressers, headquarters mission stations, government medical stations, roman catholic catecuminates, government schools, vernacular schools, and mission schools. Original map is filed in the Map/Geospatial Center, a map reproduction is attached to companion volume. "1856,8471.B-2265/625,875,8/29"
